""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" User Interface
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""

" Draw a vertical ruler at column 80
